Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)}Sergeant Major Horner, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard gunshots and advanced to capture the enemy. A child was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm very sorry, sir!\NThis'll be extra trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Burrows!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid would have died had we not rescued him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Sergeant Major made the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, abort the pincer. We're switching to maneuver warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rendezvous is at Dagger 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major, the situation\Nhas become even more severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd never leave a child to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, gentlemen, the situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up to the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because of the foxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stench of blood is gettin' stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Shenhua!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really bad if we let our source of income run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! She's gone crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, it's me, Fabiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to greet you on Young Master's strong request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, Young Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish cleaning the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is looking for his newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the plantation and pick up Young Master before it starts raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bridge is no good. The enemy could ambush us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the only road out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, kid. We're on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're American soldiers. We saved you from the shootout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect you until we reach a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't break my promises, so trust me and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roberta has taken too many drugs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is uncertain whether she will recognize Garcia at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}I've made my bet on that uncertainty.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Garcia fails to bring Roberta back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}his role will change dramatically.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need you to understand, Garcia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sergeant Major?\NYou scared out another child, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sanchez, a First Sergeant. 'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his looks, Sergeant Major Horner has a seven-year-old daughter—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is actually a really sweet daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burrows, do you have any chocolate bars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, LG might.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1150)}Oh, right. He has a sweet tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only you did not exist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only... If only you did not exist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In case Garcia successfully makes it through,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the problem is what comes next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I spent two days to let people in town know about my business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know who it is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but{\i0} that person {\i1}won't be able to overlook this situation and should definitely contact me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, he's late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LG, notify Bravo and Charlie of the new ORP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't point your gun at the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Major, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horner, you put it down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? You weren't there by coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coincidence? It's no coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took away everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who messed up our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a much worse situation than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last October, in Barinas, Venezuela,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ten people were killed at a political gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was my... my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Non-Departmental Presidential Directive 114!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took away my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And another important person to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have the right to take revenge upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Shane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to decide what to do on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is so difficult? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently four things are hidden inside that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how hard I look, it's just a picture of a hunt in a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emilione came here and boasted about it, but I bet she lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so fast to call someone a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the back side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is important to examine it from different angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here's the horned owl,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and here's the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jesus Christ! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I see it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably only looking at it from the one angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to see things correctly, you must\Napproach the matter from all possible directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your guns down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a bit rude. Who have you been waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the stuff you ordered over the phone this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been delivered to the specified location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's it going? Are things going to settle down soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it won't end just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my way here, I saw some Ivans sprinting on rooftops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We located the main U.S. Army unit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man your battle stations immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That part of the bet should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. The proud Visotoniki is making an appearance before their old enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he shoots you, he'll be considered\Nan enemy as per the rules of engagement!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear my orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! We're picking up a strange signal on our radios!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in Russian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fox! Do you hear me, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is right above you. Get ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away farther, little fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be skinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't point your guns at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is another person you broke down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the hunt is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall prepare some tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has been repelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good work, Corporal Zachamin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you and that unit on the rooftop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to the Soviet VDV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is, yes, Captain Jane Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, the Bloodhound is still close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than take on the U.S. Army and wipe each other out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balalaika will choose to settle the matter between her and Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hong Kong Triad and Hotel Moscow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once fought each other for the\Nstranglehold of power in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, to this day, neither side has claimed victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In their last duel before the ceasefire, Chang's bullet pierced through Balalaika's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she feels heavily indebted to Dutch for saving her from that predicament
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he gave her another chance to strike back at Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang is giving Balalaika deliberate openings so that she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already won that part of the gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Military radio messages we've been tapping said something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What are you going to set up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The American soldiers had their\Nground plan greatly compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they wish to return to their original mission, they lack the means to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will be there to provide for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if they give up and call off the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the right track, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of honor for the U.S. military.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll go ahead with the operation no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if all goes well, I'll have every game card\Nother than Roberta in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when the stuff you ordered from us will prove useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The U.S. government and a wealthy\NSouth American are both there to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guaranteed payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a bonanza, Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all you will take?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to have the Hong Kong Triads pay you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see where you're going. You need a backer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mafias may be promoting coexistence and co-prosperity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Chang is the one who holds the real power here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chang...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has a backer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how big the Hong Kong gangsters act, this town can only exist in collusion with the Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking for someone who can move Chang,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the true overlord of Roanapur that pulls the strings behind Chang's back, the—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to look for Leviathan in the ocean's depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you know, Rock? Not all gods are on good terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fine that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to just call him yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're covering us from above perfectly. That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's a bit rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane, are they really Soviet soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soviet Union no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she introduced herself as "Jane Doe,"\Na placeholder name for unidentified corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only wish is to leave this town of madness as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Rock...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You told me to read this when I feel lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Rock, do you understand who exactly I'm dealing with?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Rock. The boss is pissed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get too emotional with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll finish up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your friend, I don't want to see you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried about what you're trying to pull off that I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dutch, first of all, let me apologize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're polite all right, but you should've taken note of the dress code!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not wrong,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is no longer about me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're talking big, Rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you be bringing Perry Mason as your attorney or something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been commissioned for work, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A U.S. government agency is the client.\NIt's a legitimate job for the Lagoon Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This town passed the turning point long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our job is to get rid of the troublemakers at the very last moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take them out as a courier,\Nanother troublemaker will leave the town as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get what you're saying, Rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is pathetic. Right now you're just like a—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gets to put an end to all this turmoil,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll be the only ones enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's another person that needs to see a doctor, aside from the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that's never going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mr. Chang of the Triads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to commission us for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see them, Goth girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet. Isn't that Garcia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh! Our client's with the U.S. army soldiers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is being a fucking pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only a few of them right now. We can take them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. It didn't penetrate. When were you shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when that monster woman jumped down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The big one in the middle can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the black guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the captain guy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get them after my countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make a living thanks to these arms. You fuckers shot them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a message from our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war tonight is solely ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else shall interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will aim for your head or neck next time. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No trace of booby traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engine turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just followed the boy's map.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't expect to see you here, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We utilized our intelligence agents to find the town's broker agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, this might surprise you, but the cathedral on the hill was the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, nothing really surprises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also procured a ship that'll take you to the site of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad B will now merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this operation cannot be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad C will now merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete the roll call quickly, then have everyone board the vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't too pleasing, but let's accept it and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two kids now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring both of them along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that shooting, not a single policeman showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The business district is flourishing as usual five blocks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Major.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain Jane Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the assistance thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been our pleasure, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, frankly speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wish we had a chance to exchange fire with your troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that time we were still living in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since we were writhing on the sands of Afghanistan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have been eagerly looking forward to this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were in Afghanistan, eh? Vietnam was our marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We may differ in nationality or in locations we served at,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my unit has seen and fought in the same war!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:12.81,Default,,0030,0030,0000,,However, we have fallen to the point where our hopes and fears depend on a gangster's duel rather than genuine warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life of the dead is miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help but feel jealous and envious of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, we ask you to at least remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the discipline and power we maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we ask you to burn into your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sense of horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for battle! Focus the shots to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now see the major off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gun salute ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ammo annihilated target!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jane Doe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you skillfully deployed a moderate number of soldiers and carried out a saturation attack. I commend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are greatly honored by your compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if we are indeed soldiers of such caliber,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how did we end up so different from your unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me ask you a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:21:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,discharged due to illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see why you may suspect so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was practically deprived of my military position in an arbitrary discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is perfectly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a border transgression operation against international treaties,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved a child from a refugee camp, and the mass media saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was April of the year 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave this town quickly, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hope we never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is saturating, be it this town or my brain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still see a path ahead of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll manage without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are so neatly done:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,counterfeit ship registry, river passage permit, service permit for three countries, NGO activity permit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a whole set of press cards, and a heap of U.S. military night warfare equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he order all that from the Church of Violence?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, even Mr. Chang gave me a call to dispatch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There was no way I could reject it.\NWhen did he become such a top-notch negotiator?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lagoon has set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the maid is still alive, she'll leave this town to pursue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been going too well it's almost disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To deal with the war-crazed bitch, you invited, of all people, that Japanese coward,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's pulled off this much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may as well tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand why the boss regards an ex-cop like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who killed all his mates, so highly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the toughest nerves of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flatter me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.46,0:24:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we refuel on water a bit later, we'll take you to your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.55,0:24:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader, Caxton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be blunt. Can we trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.95,0:24:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy that the cyborg woman might be coming after us now, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:25:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been officially commissioned for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll fulfill the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.54,0:25:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no, I don't think that was enough to kill her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah. He's a little annoyed by all this, but you can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be familiar with this route, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.24,0:25:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Familiar"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.53,0:25:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He served in the River Boat Forces during the Vietnam War.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship will be traveling upstream on the Mekong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll enter through the Mekong Delta and travel upriver
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the border of the three countries Thailand, Burma, and Laos,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.28,0:25:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, straight to your destination, the Golden Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.00,0:25:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and also, this side of the door is my personal space. Do {\i1}not{\i0} enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.82,0:25:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Thank you for choosing to fly Bangkok Airlines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:26:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}This flight will depart Don Mueang International Airport and arrive at Mandalay International Airport at 14:30.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.42,0:26:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you. You smell terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have taken a quick shower? I know you're anxious to hunt down the foxes, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.96,0:26:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, you found the plane ticket we left at your hideout. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made arrangements so you can get past the security even if you look a bit suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.96,0:26:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The foxes will arrive in 36 hours from—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.37,0:26:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.43,0:26:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.07,0:26:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you sent by the U.S. government?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.17,0:26:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking too loud, bitch! Just shut up and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.91,0:26:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to tell you where the foxes are going! We also have vehicles ready to take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.15,0:26:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.46,0:26:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do? Well, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.55,0:26:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.71,0:26:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I kill you at the end of the hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.90,0:26:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you a painless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.57,0:27:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.01,0:27:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lay the anchor here and wait for the oiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.57,0:27:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll enter the Mekong tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.70,0:27:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.45,0:27:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No turning on the lights. Switch it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.51,0:27:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some English words.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.72,0:27:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to understand your language better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.93,0:27:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's diligent of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.88,0:27:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your Young Master doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.89,0:27:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alone on the stern deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.73,0:27:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master keeps muttering to himself that the chief is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.38,0:27:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.63,0:27:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rock's also intending to do something about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.81,0:27:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\i1}something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.28,0:27:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as you can clearly see, I'll be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, in case something goes wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to count on your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.91,0:28:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were the ones that made the request,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm beginning to think that Japanese man is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.80,0:28:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master met the U.S. Army soldiers exactly as that man arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.02,0:28:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has suffered significant mental stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I told you the other day, Rock is only good for relaxing on a bench on a sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.03,0:28:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's not the most experienced gambler,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.39,0:28:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes he bets a whole lot more than he can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.11,0:28:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think he can't handle it,\Nyou can always point that out to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.57,0:28:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.36,0:28:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.80,0:28:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too afraid to get close to him, only to discover the object of your aspiration isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.59,0:29:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiration? You don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.25,0:29:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.52,0:29:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my perspective, that man is nothing like you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.82,0:29:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not want to learn his true identity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.35,0:29:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lest you lose your fascination for him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.86,0:29:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, as you insist, he is indeed a peaceful, relaxed man\Nand those traits truly mean a lot to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.19,0:29:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you two could run away to a South American backcountry and run a cheap restaurant or the like,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.28,0:29:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet you do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.92,0:29:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.20,0:29:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were inclined to believe that I am of your kind, and that he was our polar opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.97,0:29:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for you sought salvation for yourself through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.83,0:29:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we certainly have been relying on his scheming, so I'm not practicing what I preach.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.64,0:29:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is to take Chief back and give Young Master, that boy, the peace of mind he once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.86,0:29:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it's been for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.21,0:30:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it different?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.66,0:30:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.11,0:30:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you and I are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we different, and in what way? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.04,0:30:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have those stray dog's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.56,0:30:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen countless people like you in my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.81,0:30:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were brought up in a rough family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.09,0:30:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.63,0:30:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.53,0:30:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my family was different. Dad was a frugal worker at a parking lot, and mom never tolerated sinful deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.01,0:30:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I stole a CD player my little brother wanted and got beaten up badly by my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.02,0:30:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's violence right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.94,0:30:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could definitely feel her love and affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.84,0:30:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I thought you grew up in the nastiest slum of the world's shit-hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you convinced yourself that you're the same kind of human as the Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.24,0:30:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the world look like a field of flowers to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, this is pointless. You're a plain idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.23,0:31:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.13,0:31:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.63,0:31:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with saying that to an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.47,0:31:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.53,0:31:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've convinced yourself that man is your field of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.80,0:31:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia, I'd like to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.39,0:31:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about our next plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.67,0:31:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now have all the actors on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.92,0:31:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.97,0:31:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've brought an excellent stage prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.45,0:31:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose next time, either. You're the golden key...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.46,0:31:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.61,0:32:49.61,NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,900)\blur10}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.81,0:32:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.17,0:32:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going to hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.09,0:32:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, he's going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.53,0:33:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chang is going to lose!
